==Personal life==
On 24 November 2022, Al-Rashdan was married in a wedding ceremony in his hometown [[Irbid]] attended by thousands of guests.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://sawaleif.com/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AD%D8%A7%D8%AC-%D9%85%D8%AD%D9%85%D9%88%D8%AF-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B1%D8%B4%D8%AF%D8%A7%D9%86-%D9%8A%D8%AD%D8%AA%D9%81%D9%8A-%D8%A8%D8%B2%D9%81%D8%A7%D9%81-%D8%A7%D8%A8%D9%86%D9%87-%D9%86-752375/|title=الحاج محمود الرشدان يحتفي بزفاف ابنه نزال .. صور|first=غيث|last=التل|date=November 27, 2022}}</ref> On 5 January 2024, he welcomed his firstborn child.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.sarabsport.com/2024/01/05/%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%86%D8%AC%D9%85-%D9%86%D8%B2%D8%A7%D8%B1-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B1%D8%B4%D8%AF%D8%A7%D9%86-%D9%8A%D8%AD%D8%AA%D9%81%D9%84-%D8%A8%D9%85%D9%88%D9%84%D9%88%D8%AF%D9%87-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A8%D9%83/|title=النجم نزار الرشدان يحتفل بمولوده البكر|first=دعاء|last=الموسى|date=January 5, 2024}}</ref>

